@page "/aboutus"

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Recipe App</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 85px;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #33a270;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #5a2a27; /* deep reddish-brown */
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; /* Fancy heading font */
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            letter-spacing: 1px; /* Add some spacing between letters */
        }
        h2 {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .team-photo-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around; /* evenly space out photos */
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .team-photo {
            width: 120px; /* slightly larger photo */
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            position: relative;
            border: 4px solid #5a2a27; /* thicker border color matches heading */
            margin: 0 10px; /* spacing between photos */
        }
        .team-photo::after {
            content: attr(data-name);
            position: absolute;
            min-width: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            bottom: -50px; /* lower tooltip position */
            font-size: 15px; /* larger font size */
            color: #fff; /* text color */
            background-color: #5a2a27; /* background color for text */
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(10px);
            padding: 5px 10px; /* more padding for the tooltip */
            border-radius: 5px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            visibility: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); /* subtle shadow for depth */
        }
        .team-photo:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0px);
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px; /* slightly larger paragraph text */
            padding: 0 50px; /* padding on the sides for better text block */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* space below the paragraph */
            color: #555; /* softer text color */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="team-photo-row">
            <!-- Replace image URLs with the actual paths to your images -->
            <div class="team-photo" data-name="Lillian Beck" style="background-image: url('lillian-url.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="team-photo" data-name="Ethan Lancaster" style="background-image: url('ethan-url.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="team-photo" data-name="Noah Bourque" style="background-image: url('noah-url.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="team-photo" data-name="Chris Booras" style="background-image: url('chris-url.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="team-photo" data-name="Alex Brodsky" style="background-image: url('alex-url.jpg');"></div>
        </div>
        <p>Welcome to Pushin' P(antry)! We're a group of enthusiastic chefs and computer science students from LSU committed to delivering top-notch recipes tailored to your ingredients.</p>
        <h2>Our Inspiration</h2>
        <p>We aimed to help fellow college students use the random ingredients in their fridge and pantry to create simple, easy-to-make recipes. </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
